{"tid":653831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「針咭分享」198x或之前出世既你可能無打第二次麻疹針","createTime":"2018-05-05T05:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T06:35:08.000Z","uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b98b5a24b69a6c820b7bc326ac005af03adec4ca","tid":653831,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去高危地方，搵返張針咭睇,再夾下新聞<br />\n原來1996政府先有安排小一打mmr2即係所謂既第二針<br />\n<br />\n而一般老母應該都唔知道我地呢班可憐既8x小雜種係要返健康院打多針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然話第一針都有93%抗疫力，但我地呢d賤命要去高危地區工作就緊係想再提高到97%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/134053_fe97d3df75c5c3c0f39ee5aac79218ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F134053_fe97d3df75c5c3c0f39ee5aac79218ef.png&h=54160252&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a10d2585aaa9514aaeeee753da1a71584744d236","tid":653831,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f62df063f8c94f33de30fcd6d167fb347962d8a","tid":653831,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17f57b3f788afb8257d6ba520e9ccc6b0c3262a","tid":653831,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53938d2e6f897f3e02edea4c19b9efd97081521","tid":653831,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm